mediumFindings[6]{id,severity,description,wavePrerequisite,fix}:
  MF-03,medium,"--fix --force escape hatch present in section 7 + section 10 risks but no resolution recorded. Either remove (manual resolution path) or add --yes confirmation + diff-first UX.",Wave 2,Pick one; document choice in section 5 + section 7
  MF-04,medium,"--fix --force destructive overwrite has no confirmation guard (composes with MF-03 — single resolution).",Wave 2,(co-resolved with MF-03)
  MF-05,medium,"loom-doctor TOON default rendering contract absent. commands/loom-doctor.md is a deliverable but no header/icon/footer spec exists.",Wave 2,Add rendering contract (header line + per-check icon + footer summary) to section 5 or commands/loom-doctor.md deliverable spec
  MF-06,medium,"PreToolUse hook failure footer not specified. Primary discoverability vector for existing users with failing hooks.",Wave 2,Add one-line spec: 'PreToolUse hook failure emits Tip: run /loom-doctor to diagnose hook health' to section 2 scope or section 7 remediation
  RU-01,medium,"Wave 4a runtime-equivalence.spec.ts mock boundary undefined. Plugin path mocked but the mock contract (which subprocess call gets intercepted and what fixture response) is not specified.",Wave 4a,Add fixture spec to section 5.5 describing the mock entry point (e.g. stub /plugin install loom as shell script that writes a fixture .claude-plugin/ tree)
